<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Articles | LiAlvaro Apparel</title>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Manrope:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --orange: #FF6B2B;
      --orange-deep: #E8521A;
      --bg: #FAFAFA;
      --surface: #FFFFFF;
      --border: #E5E5EA;
      --text-primary: #1D1D1F;
      --text-secondary: #6E6E73;
      --radius-lg: 24px;
      --shadow-md: 0 10px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { font-family: 'Manrope', sans-serif; background: var(--bg); color: var(--text-primary); }
    .container { max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px; }

    .topbar { background: var(--text-primary); text-align: center; padding: 9px 0; }
    .topbar p { font-size: 12.5px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.72); }
    .topbar a { color: var(--orange); text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700; }

    nav {
      position: sticky; top: 0; z-index: 50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px); background: rgba(250,250,250,0.85);
      border-bottom: 1px solid #F0F0F5; height: 56px;
    }
    .nav-inner {
      max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 40px; height: 100%;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .nav-logo img { height: 34px; display: block; width: auto; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; list-style: none; gap: 26px; }
    .nav-links a { color: var(--text-secondary); text-decoration: none; font-size: 13.5px; font-weight: 600; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }
    .nav-actions { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
    .btn-phone {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
      font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-secondary); text-decoration: none;
    }
    .btn-phone svg { width: 13px; height: 13px; }
    .btn-phone:hover { color: var(--text-primary); }
    .nav-cta {
      background: var(--orange); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 999px;
    }
    .nav-cta:hover { background: var(--orange-deep); }

    .hero {
      padding: 110px 0 70px; text-align: center; background: var(--surface);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .hero h1 { font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 70px); line-height: 1.05; letter-spacing: -0.03em; margin-bottom: 14px; }
    .hero p { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.65; }

    .section { padding: 80px 0 90px; }
    .articles-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 22px;
    }
    .article-card {
      background: #101012;
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      overflow: hidden;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: inherit;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
      transition: transform 0.22s ease, box-shadow 0.22s ease;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    }
    .article-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }
    .article-media {
      aspect-ratio: 16/9;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    }
    .article-media.one { background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.35), rgba(0,0,0,.35)), url('/images/screenprinting.jpg'); }
    .article-media.two { background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.35), rgba(0,0,0,.35)), url('/images/dtf.jpg'); }
    .article-content { padding: 22px; }
    .meta {
      color: #FF6B2B; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .08em;
      font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .article-content h2 {
      color: #ffffff;
      font-size: clamp(20px, 2.2vw, 28px);
      line-height: 1.2;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }
    .article-content p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.78); line-height: 1.65; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .read-more { color: #ffffff; font-weight: 700; }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .container, .nav-inner { padding: 0 22px; }
      .nav-links, .btn-phone { display: none; }
      .articles-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">
    <p>Same-day service available in Los Angeles · Call <a href="tel:3109042655">(310) 904-2655</a></p>
  </div>
  <nav>
    <div class="nav-inner">
      <a href="/" class="nav-logo" aria-label="LiAlvaro Home"><img src="/brand/logo.png" alt="LiAlvaro" /></a>
      <ul class="nav-links">
        <li><a href="/design-your-apparel">Design Your Apparel</a></li>
        <li><a href="/about">About Us</a></li>
        <li><a href="/#faq">FAQ</a></li>
        <li><a href="/articles">Articles</a></li>
      </ul>
      <div class="nav-actions">
        <a href="tel:3109042655" class="btn-phone">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M3.7 1C3.3 1 2.5 1.3 1.9 2L1 3c-.7.7-1 2 .3 4 .7 1.2 1.7 2.6 3.1 4s2.8 2.4 4 3.1c2 1.3 3.3 1 4 .3l1-1c.7-.7 1-1.5 1-1.9 0-.2-.2-.5-.5-.7L12 9.5c-.3-.2-.6-.3-.8-.2l-1.3.4c-.3.1-.6 0-.8-.2L7.5 8l-1.5-1.6c-.2-.2-.3-.5-.2-.8L6.2 4.4c.1-.2 0-.5-.2-.8L4.4 1.5C4.2 1.2 3.9 1 3.7 1z"/></svg>
          (310) 904-2655
        </a>
        <a href="/contact" class="nav-cta">Get a Quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Insights. Guides. Inspiration.</h1>
      <p>Everything you need to know about custom apparel from the experts in Los Angeles.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="articles-grid">
        <a href="/best-affordable-custom-t-shirt-printing-in-los-angeles-2026-local-guide" class="article-card">
          <div class="article-media one"></div>
          <div class="article-content">
            <div class="meta">Local Guide • 5 Min Read</div>
            <h2>Best Affordable Custom T-Shirt Printing in Los Angeles (2026 Local Guide)</h2>
            <p>Discover how to navigate the LA market to find high-quality prints without overspending.</p>
            <span class="read-more">Read Article →</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/the-ultimate-guide-to-finding-the-perfect-place-for-your-bulk-custom-t-shirt-event-needs" class="article-card">
          <div class="article-media two"></div>
          <div class="article-content">
            <div class="meta">Event Planning • 8 Min Read</div>
            <h2>The Ultimate Guide to Finding the Perfect Place for Your Bulk Custom T-Shirt Event Needs</h2>
            <p>Learn exactly what to look for when choosing a print partner for high-volume event orders.</p>
            <span class="read-more">Read Article →</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</body>
</html>
